metadata.name: Gnomeland #1
metadata.description: We gnomes denizens of this metaverse forest, know you because we have often come near the ETH blockchain , to protect it, and take care of you and your investments , but you have never seen us" we are happy to talk to you . and we are waiting to be collected.   We aim to immerse our Gnomes in the ever-changing development of Web3. With the help from our community, we will determine the best way to bring Gnome Land    to the forefront of the metaverse.....   8888 Gnomes all for you
